This file contains the commands used to create two containers with different
Linux distributions

Creates an Ubuntu container
docker run -it --name ubuntu --rm ubuntu:14.04 bash
Install curl
apt-get update && apt-get install curl
Checks curl version
curl --version (version 7.35)

Creates a Centos container
docker run -it --name centos --rm centos:7 bash
Install curl
yum update curl
Checks curl version
curl --version (version 7.29)

